</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Sadi.</SPEAKER>
<P>By the ma&s;s 'tis true, had forty fat monks fail'd in preach|ing Mahomet out of me, thy lips Agnos, wou'd convert me.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
