</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Lope.</SPEAKER>
<P>I know not well how that cou'd happen, for I have be&s;tow'd wonderous pams on it this three weeks, to make it &s;weet; for delicate eating, and right Malaga, there is'nt an inn can m$tch mine between this and Antiguera.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>1&s;t. <HI>Mul.</HI></SPEAKER>
<P>Ha&s;t any news &s;tirring in the&s;e parts, hone&s;t Lope.</P>
</SP>
